data.description: Nestled within the Mornington Estate community, this 2018 home is situated on an expansive .62-acre lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by hardwoods throughout the main living areas & intricate trim work that adorns the interior. The family room boasts coffered ceilings while the dining room showcases wainscoting, adding a touch of classic charm. A cozy gas fireplace in the family room provides the perfect spot for relaxation. This home features a convenient open layout, including a primary bedroom suite & a guest suite, making it ideal for both personal comfort & hosting guests. The convenience of a first-floor laundry room, complete with cabinets & tiled flooring, makes daily chores a breeze. The kitchen is a true standout, featuring gorgeous granite countertops & stainless steel appliances that convey with the property, ensuring a seamless transition into your new home. Upstairs, you'll find a generously sized secondary bedroom & a bonus room that are perfect for family or guests. The large, spacious lot provides ample room for outdoor activities, & there's even a shed in the back for additional storage.
